<a name="0">
<table align="center" border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=2 width=100%>
  <tr>
	<td bgcolor="#707070" align="left">
		<font face="Verdana,Arial,Helvetica" color="#FFFFFF" size="1">
		<STRONG>Bristlebane - Innoruuk's Wrath</STRONG> []
		·· 06-08-2000 at 07:50 PM ·· ^<a href="#top">top</a></font></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
	<td bgcolor="#202050">
	    <font face="Verdana,Arial,Helvetica" size="-2"><br>
		Innoruuk's Wrath<p>We are a new guild.  With high ideals.  Our core group is made up of <br>Dark Elves who worship Innoruk and wish to spread tyrrany, hatred, and death far and wide.  Trolls, Ogres, and Iskar are our brothers in arms.  They are also welcome to our fold.  We call All who have a soul black  as night, and a desire to belong to a collection of wicked hearted villians.  Your faction will only worsen in our company.  We offer companionship with few strings attached.  We all serve a common goal and delight in the vanquishing of our common enemies.  Any class, Any Evil race.  No membership dues.  No long meetings.  Just the occasional mass murder of helpless innocents.  Our regulars play as a group on Tuesday nights and solo throughout the week.  We'll get you in on the ground floor and see where it goes from there.<p>Gimme a tell in game<p>Necromancer Tinael<br>Favorite Son of Innoruk<br>
		<p><font size="1">
		<STRONG>- <a href="mailto:keeper@neriak.com">The Keeper</a></STRONG></font></font></td>
  </tr>
</table><p>
