	<td bgcolor="#202050">
	    <font face="Verdana,Arial,Helvetica" size="-2"><br>
		Hail, I am great Reaver Liggur of the Greenbloods, and I have gone off<br>to make my own legion, the Fallen Warlords. The Fallen Warlords is a<br>nutral/evil guild full of the following, Fighters: Warriors, Monks,<br>Shadow Knights, and Rogues. Torturers: Shadow Knights, Necromancers,<br>Shamans (No Barbarian Shamans). Healers: Shaman, Cleric (Dark Elf,<br>Erudite, and Human only). Transporters: Wizards (no High Elves). This is a semi/real roleplaying guild for the following class/race combos. send me a tell on brell for more detail.<p>----Reaver of Darkness, employed by the Greenbloods. of the<br>official (Greenblood given) season on the fourth. Liggur----
		<p><font size="1">
		<STRONG>- <a href="mailto:keeper@neriak.com">The Keeper</a></STRONG></font></font></td>
